接口 SearchOperationListener

  • 所有已知实现类:

    public interface SearchOperationListener
    An listener for search, fetch and context events.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明

      A Composite listener that multiplexes calls to each of the listeners methods.

    • 方法详细资料

      • onPreQueryPhase

        default void onPreQueryPhase(SearchContext searchContext)
        Executed before the query phase is executed
        参数:
        searchContext - the current search context

      • onFailedQueryPhase

        default void onFailedQueryPhase(SearchContext searchContext)
        Executed if a query phased failed.
        参数:
        searchContext - the current search context

      • onQueryPhase

        default void onQueryPhase(SearchContext searchContext,
                          long tookInNanos)
        Executed after the query phase successfully finished. Note: this is not invoked if the query phase execution failed.
        参数:
        searchContext - the current search context
        tookInNanos - the number of nanoseconds the query execution took
        另请参阅:
        onFailedQueryPhase(SearchContext)

      • onPreFetchPhase

        default void onPreFetchPhase(SearchContext searchContext)
        Executed before the fetch phase is executed
        参数:
        searchContext - the current search context

      • onFailedFetchPhase

        default void onFailedFetchPhase(SearchContext searchContext)
        Executed if a fetch phased failed.
        参数:
        searchContext - the current search context

      • onFetchPhase

        default void onFetchPhase(SearchContext searchContext,
                          long tookInNanos)
        Executed after the fetch phase successfully finished. Note: this is not invoked if the fetch phase execution failed.
        参数:
        searchContext - the current search context
        tookInNanos - the number of nanoseconds the fetch execution took
        另请参阅:
        onFailedFetchPhase(SearchContext)

      • onNewContext

        default void onNewContext(SearchContext context)
        Executed when a new search context was created
        参数:
        context - the created context

      • onFreeContext

        default void onFreeContext(SearchContext context)
        Executed when a previously created search context is freed. This happens either when the search execution finishes, if the execution failed or if the search context as idle for and needs to be cleaned up.
        参数:
        context - the freed search context

      • onNewScrollContext

        default void onNewScrollContext(SearchContext context)
        Executed when a new scroll search SearchContext was created
        参数:
        context - the created search context

      • onFreeScrollContext

        default void onFreeScrollContext(SearchContext context)
        Executed when a scroll search SearchContext is freed. This happens either when the scroll search execution finishes, if the execution failed or if the search context as idle for and needs to be cleaned up.
        参数:
        context - the freed search context

      • validateSearchContext

        default void validateSearchContext(SearchContext context,
                                   TransportRequest transportRequest)
        Executed prior to using a SearchContext that has been retrieved from the active contexts. If the context is deemed invalid a runtime exception can be thrown, which will prevent the context from being used.
        参数:
        context - the context retrieved from the active contexts
        transportRequest - the request that is going to use the search context
